body: "CONTEXT: Commander flags, MCP tool schemas, and pm contracts output all need overlapping schema data. DECISION: cli-contracts.ts (and cli-contracts/*) is the single truth; *_FLAG_CONTRACTS drive Commander, PM_TOOL_ACTION_SCHEMA_CONTRACTS drive both the lazy MCP schema Proxy and pm contracts; startup cost deferred via lazy Proxy. CONSEQUENCES: no CLI/MCP drift, always-accurate contracts; a single large file; new flags need coordinated edits across flag contracts + schema contracts + parameter tables (checklist in memory). EVIDENCE: src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts createLazyContractSchema; items pm-3mal/pm-p8j6/pm-xlzl."
